Lepaskan kami!  - Ajeet!

00:02:50.720 --> 00:02:52.480
Ajeet, kamu mau kemana?
- Ajeet!

00:02:53.720 --> 00:02:55.280
Apa yang sedang kamu lakukan?

00:02:56.720 --> 00:02:58.520
Ini ilegal.

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:06.960
Jangan berani-berani
menyentuh anggota keluarga kami.

00:03:10.360 --> 00:03:11.520
Ajeet!

00:03:12.920 --> 00:03:14.120
Ajeet!

00:03:15.240 --> 00:03:16.360
Paman!

00:03:16.920 --> 00:03:17.960
Ajeet!

00:03:23.640 --> 00:03:25.280
Tolong, Ajeet!  - Ajeet!

